  <li>Toggle the toolbar to allow you to enter urls: option-command-T</li>
  <li>Create a new tab: command-T</li>
  <li>Copy paste your url: http://<%=request.domain%>/scripts/&lt;<span style="color:#f00;">twitter_id</span>&gt;.user.js</li>
  <li>Click yes, please install and take over my computer</li>
  <li>Refresh the page: command-R</li>
  <li>Enjoy</li>
</ol>

